                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Williams</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Rockhill</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-04-24"><hi rend="italic">April 24, 1896</hi></date>.
                                (Received 4.50 p.m.)</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Superior court yesterday quashed charges against Sanguily of being
                            concerned in kidnaping Fernandez Castro.</p>
